headline: Fifth Third Bancorp Announces Cash Dividends
summary: CINCINNATI, December 10, 2024--Today Fifth Third Bancorp announced the declaration of cash dividends on its common shares, Series H preferred shares, Series I preferred shares, Series J preferred shares, Series K preferred shares, Series L preferred shares, and Class B Series A preferred shares.
